{"id": "1521407668651167744", "channel_id": "1521407668651167744", "author_id": "411703528831188993", "author_name": "rhizaea", "content": "Very minor bug. In alternate difficulties (Story, Hard), the cover art for chapters not yet unlocked gets duplicated once over, pushing everything back one. For example, in the first screenshot the Chapter 6 art is shown for both Chapter 6 and Chapter 7, and Chapter 8 shows Chapter 7's cover art. In the second screenshot you can see how everything shows the cover art for the chapter before it.", "timestamp": "2026-06-30T06:50:54.594000+00:00", "thread_id": "1521407668651167744", "reactions": [{"emoji": "Winkle_omg", "emoji_id": "1468257899330539774", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1521407669100089455", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 4158244, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1521407668651167744/1521407669100089455/image.png?ex=6a45618e&is=6a44100e&hm=f31b14f288d5e272396ea5b0bd56e4d73b9ded2407bf328181f11f5d2b58bb50&"}, {"id": "1521407669586362368", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 4642648, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1521407668651167744/1521407669586362368/image.png?ex=6a45618e&is=6a44100e&hm=c8d4c1b26da2dff1e8276e90cf6ee8ab72872cf79e7df9b128003e2c63eb68fa&"}]}
{"id": "1521375473056088094", "channel_id": "1521375473056088094", "author_id": "111382919502684160", "author_name": "foxblood13", "content": "It should be a set song for all menus. Entering and exiting menus is just a bunch of noise because the song is always changing or getting cut off. \n\nThe event music when you select them plays on top of the song and is really loud in comparison.  \n\nEven getting a WoD from event currency forces the song to start over right after. \n\nShop music completely cuts it off so the song starts over as soon as you leave.\n\nBanner menu cuts it off completely.\n\nCurriculum cuts it off completely.\n\nIt all feels like it defeats the purpose of setting anything yourself.  I think I'd rather turn  off game sound completely than hear the beginning of a song starting over and over again or a few seconds of other random menu music.\n\nIt would be really nice to set music / playlists for something like d-tide stages or the train.", "timestamp": "2026-06-30T04:42:58.566000+00:00", "thread_id": "1521375473056088094", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-30T05:00:02.075000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}]}
